    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that delivers great value? This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs and drives smoothly, with a clean interior and an exterior that presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use. The mechanicals are in solid shape, making this a great choice for anyone who wants dependability without paying mint-condition prices. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 33500.0,
